redcap:Reports.title: Expiring CVs (within 30 days)
redcap:Reports.description:
This report lists CVs which have expired, or will expire within the next 30 days. You can adjust the number of days in the future to check by adjusting the following filter code under Step 3 of the report editor: 
datediff("today", [cv_expiry][last-instance], "d", TRUE) <   = 30

redcap:Reports.title: Expiring GCP certificates (within 180 days)
redcap:Reports.description:
This report lists GCP certificates which have expired, or will expire within the next 180 days. You can adjust the number of days in the future to check by adjusting the following filter code under Step 3 of the report editor: 
datediff("today", [gcp_expiry][last-instance], "d", TRUE) <    = 180

redcap:Reports.title: Expiring IATA certificates (within 90 days)
redcap:Reports.description:
This report lists IATA certificates which have expired, or will expire within the next 90 days. You can adjust the number of days in the future to check by adjusting the following filter code under Step 3 of the report editor: 
datediff("today", [iata_expiry][last-instance], "d", TRUE) <    = 90

redcap:Reports.title: Expiring licences/registrations (30 days)
redcap:Reports.description:
This report lists AHPRA registrations which have expired, or will expire within the next 30 days. You can adjust the number of days in the future to check by adjusting the following filter code under Step 3 of the report editor: 
datediff("today", [licence_expiry][last-instance], "d", TRUE) <   = 30
